commit.message: Undoing recent macos changes.
Reverting recent macOS changes.
Updating changes doc.
Migrating from Quartz to Rubicon. Thanks to Russell Keith-Magee for this code.
Adding the KEYEVENTF_KEYDOW constant to Windows.

Removing _window_win.py because it hasn't been needed for quite some time. (PyGetWindow does all of its functionality.)

Removing commented-out code from _pyautogui/_pyautogui_win.py because it was confusing. (There was no actual bug caused by it.)
Merge branch 'master' of github.com:asweigart/pyautogui
Bug fix for the apps key in Linux. Fixed the short description of the package.
